Therapist- (4)
- The therapist has the ability to talk to a person each night, to reduce their respawn time by 2 phases before they die. 
- They can do this until the respawn time of a person drops to 2 phases. Any attempts beyond that will fail. The person is informed that a therapist had talked to them.
- After a person respawns, their respawn times are set back to normal. 
- Therapy is a night end action. Action fails if the person is killed before the therapy session. Therapy is not visiting action. 
- Respawns in 6 phases.
